### Power Up Ideas
 - bonus ball

### Cheat Key Ideas
 - a key to add bonus points
 - "p" to pause, then "c" for continue

### Something Extra
 - "bonus ball" round, where extra balls can be shot from the paddle
  and can contribute to breaking bricks, but not losing lives
